<p>火箭得到：朗佐-鲍尔，雷迪克，布莱索和未来首轮选秀权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201129/f57c19168b7b492981233885886372a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
